## 七、备份与维护

### 7.1 数据库备份

创建定时备份脚本 `/opt/rental/backup/backup-db.sh`：

```bash
#!/bin/bash
BACKUP_DIR=/opt/rental/backup
DB_NAME=rental
DB_USER=rental
DB_PASSWORD=your_password_here
DATE=$(date +%Y%m%d_%H%M%S)

mysqldump -u$DB_USER -p$DB_PASSWORD $DB_NAME | gzip > $BACKUP_DIR/db_$DATE.sql.gz

# 保留最近 30 天备份，删除更早的
find $BACKUP_DIR -name "db_*.sql.gz" -mtime +30 -delete
```

```bash
chmod +x /opt/rental/backup/backup-db.sh

# 添加到 crontab（每天凌晨 3 点执行）
crontab -e
0 3 * * * /opt/rental/backup/backup-db.sh
```

### 7.2 媒体文件备份

```bash
# 定期同步媒体文件到备份目录
rsync -av /data/rental/media/ /opt/rental/backup/media/
```

